description: Decadent mason jar desserts served from a rockin' vintage camper named Pearl.Whether catering a corporate event, baby shower, birthday party, graduation, oyster roast, or even the oh so chic Charleston wedding, we'll partner with you from beginning to end to tailor a delicious dessert menu to suit any palate.We'll even custom tailor labels and our oh so adorable Birchwood tasting spoons for your special occasion.
name: Sweet Lulu's Bakery On Wheels
